| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0576 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9eb0042e-9ef2-50f5-bb80-904e29fc4fb6"
